    User
    The User class represents a user with attributes such as name, email, birthdate, gender, and CPF, and overrides the equals and hashCode methods to compare and hash based on the CPF attribute.
    UserRelation
    This is a Java class representing a user relation entity with a primary key and methods for checking equality and generating hash codes.
